Package: mysql-python-py22
Version: 0.9.2
Revision: 1
Source: mirror:sourceforge:mysql-python/MySQL-python-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: afef758f56289f98408dd9f379d8fc8d
BuildDepends: python22 | python22-nox, mysql12-dev
Depends: python22 | python22-nox, mysql12-shlibs
Patch: mysql-python.patch
SetCFLAGS: -I%p/include/mysql
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib/mysql
CompileScript: <<
  %p/bin/python2.2 setup.py build
<<
InstallScript: <<
  %p/bin/python2.2 setup.py install --prefix=%i
  mkdir -p %i/share/doc/%n
  cp -R doc %i/share/doc/%n
<<
DocFiles: CHANGELOG MANIFEST PKG-INFO README
Description: Python interface to MySQL (for python 2.2.x)
DescDetail: <<
Python interface to MySQL

MySQLdb is an interface to the popular MySQL database server for Python.
The design goals are:
- Compliance with Python database API version 2.0
- Thread-safety
- Thread-friendliness (threads will not block each other)
- Compatibility with MySQL-3.23 and later
<<
